        "**Find the partial derivatives**: First, we need to find the partial derivatives of the paraboloid equation with respect to x and y:\n",
        "\n",
        "âˆ‚z/âˆ‚x = 2(x - 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "âˆ‚z/âˆ‚y = 2y\n",
        "\n",
        "**Evaluate the partial derivatives at point P**: Next, we evaluate these partial derivatives at the point P(1, 0, 1):\n",
        "\n",
        "âˆ‚z/âˆ‚x (1, 0, 1) = 2(1 - 1) = 0\n",
        "\n",
        "âˆ‚z/âˆ‚y (1, 0, 1) = 2(0) = 0\n",
